headline: Gilead Sciences Stock Gains 21% YTD: Buy, Sell or Hold?
summary: GILD stock jumps 21.1% YTD as HIV dominance, lenacapavir progress, and liver drug approval offset oncology pressures. However, we recommend investors remain on the sidelines at current levels.
